Squares of sorted arrays:

Link: https://leetcode.com/problems/squares-of-a-sorted-array/description/

Code: (Brute Force):

class Solution {
    public int[] sortedSquares(int[] nums) {
        for(int i=0;i<nums.length;i++){
            nums[i]=nums[i]*nums[i];
        }
        Arrays.sort(nums);
        return nums;
    }
}

Time complexity: O(nlogn)
